title: Singing road strikes wrong chord in Dutch village
text:
Singing road strikes wrong chord in Dutch village 8:39pm BST - 00:56 
Residents of Jelsum are bothered by the never-ending cacophony created by a local highway that ''sings'' when motorists hit the road. Elly Park reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
